<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.3">
<l>cuṟṟu moḷivaṭṭam cūḻntu cōti paranteṅku</l>
<l>mettaṉai ceyyilum eṉma kaṉmukam nērovvāy</l>
<l>vittakaṉ vēṅkaṭa vāṇaṉ uṉṉai viḷikkiṉṟa</l>
<l>kaittalam nōvāmē yampu līkaṭi tōṭivā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Big Moon, revolving halo of light circling [the sky] spreading light everywhere,</l>
<l>However much you do, you are no match [for] my son’s face.</l>
<l>Without injuring the palms of the sage resident in Vēṇkaṭha</l>
<l>that summon you, come running quickly!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
